<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home</title>
    <!-- <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"> -->
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .heading {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #333;
            text-align: center;
        }

        p {
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #666;
        }

        .blog-post {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .blog-post h1 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #333;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .blog-post p {
            color: #555;
        }

        .read-more {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 6px 13px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            background-color: #6cbf84;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .read-more:hover {
            background-color: #4a9c60;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include("header") %>
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="heading">Home</h1>
        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Nisi non a rerum ut cum assumenda minima lsci eos, rem odio qui maiores reiciendis ipsam corporis possimus tenetur incbcaecati fuga? Laudantium dolores esse quo unde laboriosam mollitia corrupti vitae totam, enim adipisci quod architecto quia possimus nemo consequuntur iusto, quam voluptatem omnis exercitationem, quis consectetur soluta eaque culpa eum. Quas soluta eligendi fugiat excepturi repellat dolorem numquam veritatis unde ex maxime! Eum error accusantium ipsum voluptatum, reprehenderit minima in perferendis dicta tenetur architecto eos nam praesentium dignissimos iusto iste nesciunt deleniti sit veniam distinctio pariatur harum? Aliquid laboriosam iste nobis eligendi nisi distinctio? Nobis culpa voluptatem reprehenderit, tenetur error, tempora suscipit ratione nostrum asperiores dignissimos doloremque quaerat quis nisi neque qui quidem adipisci nam? Sint ad impedit voluptas.</p>

        <% if (array.length > 0) { %>
            <% array.forEach(function(object) { %>
                <div class="blog-post">
                    <h1><%= object.title %></h1>
                    <p><%= object.content.substring(0, 100) %>... <a class="read-more" href="/blogs/<%=object.title%>">Read More</a></p>
                </div>
            <% }) %>
        <% } %>
    </div>
    <%- include("footer") %>
</body>

</html>
